      "asbval:evidence_quote": "IDSL_MINT was developed upon the transformer model architecture originally proposed by Vaswani et al. [17] and is implemented within the python PyTorch framework (https://pytorch.org)... IDSL_MINT was developed using Python 3.10 and implemented with PyTorch 2.0... GPUs and CPUs are both supported by IDSL_MINT.",
